            <sentence>
                <offset>159</offset>
                <text>At the age of 16 months, his weight was 10.75 kg (25th percentile), height 78 cm (10th percentile), head circumference 46 cm (10th percentile), inner canthal distance 3 cm (90th percentile) and outer canthal distance was 8.5 cm (90th percentile).</text>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>406</offset>
